description_text:
[A] service runs in two sections:
1. Between Inwood-207 St and Euclid Av
2. Between Howard Beach-JFK Airport and Far Rockaway-Mott Av

shuttle bus icon Free shuttle buses run along two routes:
1. Local buses make all stops between Euclid Av and Lefferts Blvd/Howard Beach-JFK Airport
2. Express buses run between Euclid Av and Howard Beach-JFK Airport, (Euclid Av-bound buses make a stop at Aqueduct-N Conduit Av)
Transfer between [A] trains and shuttle bus icon buses at Euclid Av and/or Howard Beach-JFK Airport accessibility icon.
Note: All trains at Howard Beach-JFK Airport board from the Manhattan-bound platform.

Travel tip:
For AirTrain JFK, use the Sutphin Blvd-Archer Av-JFK Airport accessibility icon | [E][J]. Transfer to/from [J] at Broadway Junction.
In Manhattan, take the [E] instead.

header_text: No [N] between 39 Av-Dutch Kills, Queens and 57 St-7 Av, Manhattan
description_text:

1. Shuttle train between Ditmars Blvd and 39 Av-Dutch Kills, every 12 mins days/evenings
2. Between Coney Island and 57 St-7 Av, and via the [Q] to/from 96 St, every 15 mins days/evenings

shuttle bus icon Free Q108 shuttle buses run between 39 Av-Dutch Kills and Queens Plaza.

Travel Alternatives: (see a map of this service change)
For service between Queens and Manhattan, take the [E][F] or [R].

For 39 Av-Dutch Kills, take shuttle bus icon free shuttle buses to/from Queens Plaza [E][R] or use the nearby 36 St [R] station for service to/from Manhattan.

For Queensboro Plaza, use nearby Queens Plaza.

For 5 Av/59 St and Lexington Av/59 St, take the [R] days and evenings.
Consider using nearby stations at Lexington Av/63 St [Q] ([N]), or the [4][5][6] at 59 St.

When exiting at 39 Av-Dutch Kills, 36 St or Queens Plaza request a GO Ticket for re-entry into the subway.

header_text: In Queens, Manhattan-bound [7] skips 111 St and 82 St-Jackson Hts
description_text:
Use nearby 103 St-Corona Plaza, 90 St-Elmhurst Av or 74 St-Broadway stations.

Additional travel alternatives:
For service to 111 St, take the [7] to 103 St-Corona Plaza and transfer to a Flushing-bound [7].

For service to 82 St-Jackson Hts, take the [7] to 74 St-Broadway and transfer to a Flushing-bound [7].

For service from these stations, take the [7] to 90 St-Elmhurst Av or Mets-Willets Point, and transfer to a Manhattan-bound [7].

For 111 St, connect between the [7] and Q48 and at Mets-Willets Point.
For 82 St-Jackson Hts, connect between the [7] and Q32 at 74 St-Broadway.
